\sum_{n=1}^\infty y_n
S_N = \displaystyle \sum_{n=1}^{N} y_n = \displaystyle \sum_{n=1}^{N} (x_n - x_{n+1}) = (x_1 - x_2) + (x_2 - x_3) + \cdots + (x_N - x_{N+1}) = x_1 - x_{N+1}
\displaystyle \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} y_n = \lim_{N \rightarrow \infty} S_N = \lim_{N \rightarrow \infty} (x_1 - x_{N+1}) = x_1 - x
